  * P_MXDC_S0PAGE_RESOURCE_ESCAPE_T pS0PageResourceEscapeData = 
  *                         (P_MXDC_S0PAGE_RESOURCE_ESCAPE_T)HeapAlloc(
  *                             GetProcessHeap(),
  *                             0,
  *                             iTotalDataSize);
  * ```
  * 
  * 
  * 
